#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.221"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.221:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 22. Sāmaññavagga → dutiyavaggo (s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.221:0.2"
msgid "22. Sāmaññavagga "
msgstr "22. Similarity "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.221:0.3"
msgid "221 "
msgstr "221. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.221:1.1"
msgid "“Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "“Someone with ten qualities is cast down to hell. "

msgctxt "an10.221:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.221:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātī hoti, adinnādāyī hoti, kāmesumicchācārī hoti, musāvādī hoti, pisuṇavāco hoti, pharusavāco hoti, samphappalāpī hoti, abhijjhālu hoti, byāpannacitto hoti, micchādiṭṭhiko hoti—"
msgstr "They kill living creatures, steal, and commit sexual misconduct. They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. And they’re covetous, malicious, with wrong view. "

msgctxt "an10.221:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "Someone with these ten qualities is cast down to hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.304, sc2
msgctxt "an10.221:2.1"
msgid "Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge. "
msgstr "Someone with ten qualities is raised up to heaven. "

msgctxt "an10.221:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.221:2.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti, anabhijjhālu hoti, abyāpannacitto hoti, sammādiṭṭhiko hoti—"
msgstr "They don’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual misconduct. They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. They’re contented, kind-hearted, with right view. "

msgctxt "an10.221:2.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti. "
msgstr "Someone with these ten qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
